    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53672944/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53672944-20.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53672944/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">喵了个咪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-22"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-22 10:22:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8096519_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   对于宋朝的理解，多年来一直停留在课本和评书故事的印象里，比如狸猫换太子、岳飞传、靖康耻、澶渊之盟等等，就连《水浒传》这样的小说，描述的都是宋朝的腐败和无能。翻开著名宋史研究者吴钩的大作《原来你是这样的宋朝》，顿时感觉到一股清新之气，冲破了以往陈旧的观念，忍...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8096519/#comments">(13回应)</a>
